modName: CBBE Female Save Pack - Dawnguard edition
descriptionHtml:
This is save pack of fresh save game jsut insade Helgen Keep with Hadvar.
I used CBBE body so You must have this. Also for hairstyles download Oblivion hair pack. And I play with Dawnguard DLC.
Character You can play:
1. Marjolean Nord mage
2. Janesa Breton warrior
3. Alessia Imperial thief/assasin
4. Ashera gra-Thelin Orc barbarian
5. Kazani Redguard duelist/spellsword
Mod You need to download to have the same girl :
1. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666 CBBE body
2. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22598 Oblivion hair pack
3. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812 for the same face
4. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21369 for war paints
5. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10251 Silverlight armor
6. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14035 cloth edition od Silverlight
7. http://oblivion.nexusmods.com/mods/30708 Silverlight retex
optional mod I used:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22793 morrowind armor
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21572 blood with armor
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23165 avatar of Grenth

Also You must have patch 1.7 and optional Dawnguar DLC.
Download, play, enjoy and rate.
Credits in special section.
author: kreator86
